Note on the dataset:

The skills in this package were distilled from the public HuggingFace dataset
`Kuberwastaken/Fable-5-traces` (4,665 rows, 60 sessions) under the terms of
its original license. The distilled skills themselves — written in our own
words from observed patterns — are licensed under the MIT license above.

Claude, Fable 5, and Anthropic are trademarks of Anthropic PBC. This project
is not affiliated with or endorsed by Anthropic. MiniMax is a trademark of
MiniMax Inc. This project is not affiliated with or endorsed by MiniMax.
